        <strong style="font-size:0.95rem;">What is Gender Identity? The Gender Spectrum</strong>
        <p style="opacity:0.6;font-size:0.83rem;margin:0.4rem 0 0;line-height:1.4;">An evidence-based guide to gender identity. Learn the difference between sex and gender, understand terminology like tra...</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</SiteLayout>